# 06 - Essay Writer
# Write a structured essay on any topic

NAME essay-writer
INPUT topic
INPUT style DEFAULT "academic"
INPUT word_count DEFAULT 1000

GOAL outline "Create a detailed outline for a $word_count-word $style essay about $topic. Include thesis, main points, and conclusion structure."
GOAL draft "Write the full essay following the outline. Match the $style tone throughout."
GOAL polish "Review and improve: fix grammar, improve flow, strengthen arguments, and ensure coherence."

RUN write USING outline, draft, polish
